data.description: This completely renovated beauty could be exactly what you've been looking for! Enter to find a bright and beautiful living room with recessed lighting, brand new floors and large bow window illuminating natural sunlight throughout. The dining room features a charming chandelier and wood accent. The kitchen is equipped with slate appliances, gorgeous white cabinetry and granite counter tops. There are three great size bedrooms, all with brand new brand new wall-to-wall carpet. The master bedroom is complete with a full master bathroom and plenty of closet space! The basement is finished with separate utility area and could easily be converted into an additional bedroom/family room or home office. There is a rear deck, perfect for entertaining and a garage for off-street parking convenience. Additional upgrades include updated plumbing, electric and brand new HVAC. Come see all that this beauty has to offer, schedule your showings today.
